## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture all perspectives on the issue. The data and opinions gathered are subject to the biases of the sources. Additionally, cultural and legal contexts vary significantly across different regions, which may affect the applicability of these findings in specific locales. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the implications of legalizing divorce.